{
  "stem": "22586.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Essen?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister and two sisters, who-- one of them went to school with me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Their name was Rene and Agnes Konigsberg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were with us all along.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In fact, when-- when my sister and I were picked out to go to work in Essen, they did not pick-- the-- the two of them were-- had typhus in Gelsenkirchen.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they were very sickly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were not picked to go to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said to one of the men who picked me out that I am not going unless they can come with us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he let-- he had them come also.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they came with us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We all stayed together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we sort of looked out for each other.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The four of us stayed together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When, for instance, in sleeping on the floor in the winter was very cold, and since we just had that one dress and one blanket, no coat, but one blanket, so the blanket served as a cover for at night and also as a coat for during the day.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so one blanket was not warm enough.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So the four of us would sleep together and put the four blankets together.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That way all of us were warm enough, or kept each other warm.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And-- we-- one-- one day in the winter, I remember a very snowy, very cold winter, as we-- I mentioned before, I think, that on December 12, there was a bombing.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And our camp was bombed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And also in town, the train that we used to take, the streetcar, was bombed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So it was out of commission.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So from then on, we had to march to work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We went by foot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had to get up even earlier, because it was seven kilometers each way.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
